    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car from day one\u2014always kept it in the garage and made sure it stayed spotless. It drives like an absolute dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all!",
