    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This 2006 Mitsubishi Lancer Evolution IX MR is a preserved specimen of rally-bred engineering. The 4G63 MIVEC powerplant maintains exceptional vacuum at idle, with the twin-scroll TD05HR turbo spooling exactly to factory specifications. The drivetrain features the sophisticated Active Center Differential (ACD) and a precise 6-speed close-ratio transmission, both operating without hesitation. Suspension remains true to its MR heritage with original Bilstein monotube dampers providing sharp turn-in response. Every VIN tag is present on the original panels, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation. This is a mechanically flawless example for a serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Garage kept. Zero accidents. Original factory paint. Clean title in hand. Interior is spotless. All maintenance records available.",
      "price": 44000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a truly collector-grade 2018 BMW M3 Competition in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen rain or snow. The Yas Marina Blue Metallic exterior is flawless, featuring a professional-grade ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like finish; there are no rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks. The interior is equally pristine, with Silverstone Extended Merino Leather that shows no signs of bolster wear or aging. It has never been smoked in and retains its original factory scent. Mechanically, the car is in peak form, boasting a comprehensive service history exclusively performed at authorized dealerships. We recently completed a major service including all fluid flushes and the installation of four new Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. This M3 is entirely stock, never modified or tracked, and comes with the original window sticker, two keys, and all service receipts. For the buyer seeking a 'as-new' driving experience, this example is unparalleled.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile complemented by a pristine, wear-free interior. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been meticulously preserved, offering the discerning collector a rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar that is indistinguishable from its original delivery state. This is, without reservation, the finest example currently available on the market.",
      "price": 47850.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty \u2013 it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it is looking absolutely flawless. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection inside and out. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next big adventure. Come take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
