      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six remains mechanically flawless, delivering linear power through its individual throttle bodies with the signature high-RPM metallic rasp. The double-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe\u2014a critical structural point\u2014has been reinforced to ensure long-term chassis rigidity. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The suspension geometry is perfectly dialed, featuring fresh bushings and OEM dampers that eliminate unsprung weight chatter and parasitic steering play. Every component, from the cooling system's expansion tank to the cross-drilled rotors, reflects a rigorous maintenance pedigree. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the purist who demands mechanical precision and uncompromised atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
